name: HubCap
description: A hubcap or hub cap is a decorative disk on an automobile wheel that covers at minimum the central portion of the wheel

name: Spoiler
description: A spoiler is an automotive aerodynamic device whose intended design function is to 'spoil' unfavorable air movement across a body of a vehicle

name: Hood
description: A car hood, also referred to as a bonnet in some other countries, is the hinged cover that rests over the engine of a front-engine vehicle.
